text:
Maia Mitchell (born 18 August 1993) is an Australian actress and singer. She is known for her roles as Brittany Flune in the children's television series "Mortified" for the Nine Network, and as Natasha Ham in the Seven Network's teen drama "Trapped".
Mitchell starred in the Freeform drama "The Fosters" as Callie Adams Foster. She also co-starred in the Disney Channel original movies "Teen Beach Movie" and "Teen Beach 2" as McKenzie.
